
The *ctrl-alt-delete* keyboard sequence is also referred to as *Secure Authentication Sequence* (short: SAS).

This sequence is handled by → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/winlogon_exe[winlogon.exe].

After pressiong this sequence, the user is presented with the following options:
  • → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/user32_dll/LockWorkStation[Lock]
  • Switch → Windows/user-account[user]
  • Sign out
  • Change a → development/security/password
  • → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/Taskmgr_exe[Task Manager]
